duplicate_route_label: [Duplicate Route Label] The route entry has a label that has already been added.
route_missing_name: [Route Missing Name] The route entry is missing the name property.
invalid_route_type: [Invalid Route Type] The route type must be one of three values; router, middleware or app.
missing_router_middleware: [Missing Router or Middleware] An app entry has a param, router or middleware dependency that doesn't exist.
missing_required_dependency: [Missing Required Dependency] A required param, middleware, or router is missing, verify the dependency exists or remove the dependency from the meta data.
